SUMMARY:Mother's Day Native Art Market
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the amazing caregivers in your life at the Mother’s Day Native Art Market!  \n\n\nJoin us at the Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center to shop unique jewelry\, prints\, art\, and more directly from talented Native creators. We encourage you to Shop Native & Shop Local this season!  \n\n\n When: May 9th & 10th\, 2026 Time: 10:00 AM to 5:00 PM Location: 5011 Bernie Whitebear Way\, Seattle\, 98199 \n\n#ShopNative #ShopLocal #MothersDay #NativeArt #ShopLocalSeattle #SeattleEvents
URL:https://unitedindians.org/event/mother/2026-05-10/
LOCATION:Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center\, 5011 Bernie Whitebear Way\, Seattle\, WA\, 98199\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://unitedindians.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Native-Art-Market-Mother-Day-Print.png
END:VEVENT
